=A0
While we are on the topic of pronunciation, I am ma=
king the points as I see them and with full force of conviction. But it is =
important to realize that this is only 1% important. God comes easier to a =
devoted dunce with laughable mistakes than to a proud scholar with enviable=
 perfection. Cultivate devotion, humility, surrender, fascination and love =
for god. That is billion times more important than correct pronunciation. H=
owever, IF someone cares, I gave enough hints based on my opinion above.
=
=A0
Several years back, I discovered mistakes in my own pronunciation one a=
fter the other and corrected them. No single region of India is perfect, bu=
t, if you look at everyone and think with commonsense, you can figure every=
thing out. Also, there are ample clues in the grammar rules.
=A0
I used to =
want to shoot a small video on these errors and post it on internet, for th=
e benefit of others. But, with the realization that there are other importa=
nt things that people should worry about first, this fell off my radar..

